Margaret Joslin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margaret_Joslin 0 Margaret Joslin (6 August 1883 – 14 October 1956) was an American film actress. She appeared in 166 films between 1910 and 1923. She was born Cleveland, Ohio and died in Glendale, California. She was married to comedian Harry Todd. Margaret_Joslin ( 6_August_1883 – 14_October_1956 ) was an_American_film_actress .
